  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starpuffs is a cute puzzle game where you solve increasingly challenging puzzles with just one deceptively simple movement mechanic.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Cloudy, a pink ball of fluff who is home to the bright and sleepy Starpuffs. One night, when Cloudy and the Starpuffs are sound asleep, a flurry of wind sweeps the Starpuffs away! You need to rescue them, but it won’t be easy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Cloudy sideways to split into little Cloudies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move up or down to split again into mini Cloudies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.poster.avif?t=1763978190\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.webm?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.mp4?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When two Cloudies from the same split meet, they merge together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue all your Starpuffs and merge back into big Cloudy in order to give everyone a good night's sleep!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.poster.avif?t=1763978190\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.webm?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.mp4?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 unique zones, each with its own vibrant atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >125 levels  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New environmental mechanics with each zone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colourful, fun and challenging gameplay with cute characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >W A S D, Arrow Keys or Gamepad Joystick/D-pad to move</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starpuffs is a cute puzzle game where you solve increasingly challenging puzzles with just one deceptively simple movement mechanic.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Cloudy, a pink ball of fluff who is home to the bright and sleepy Starpuffs. One night, when Cloudy and the Starpuffs are sound asleep, a flurry of wind sweeps the Starpuffs away! You need to rescue them, but it won’t be easy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Cloudy sideways to split into little Cloudies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move up or down to split again into mini Cloudies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.poster.avif?t=1763978190\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.webm?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/1f67cc92036aaaa0537a55c9a9aaf07d.mp4?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When two Cloudies from the same split meet, they merge together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue all your Starpuffs and merge back into big Cloudy in order to give everyone a good night's sleep!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.poster.avif?t=1763978190\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.webm?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651050/extras/51ce6f0617b7a486013e7c5b66d90025.mp4?t=1763978190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 unique zones, each with its own vibrant atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >125 levels  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New environmental mechanics with each zone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colourful, fun and challenging gameplay with cute characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >W A S D, Arrow Keys or Gamepad Joystick/D-pad to move</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
